  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Main] Trash up to 3 cards in your hand. For each card
    trashed by this effect, \uFF1CDe-Digivolve 1\uFF1E 1 of your opponent's Digimon.
    (Trash 1 card from the top of one of your opponent's Digimon. If it has no digivolution
    cards, or becomes a level 3 Digimon, you can't trash any more cards.) Then, delete
    1 of your opponent\u2019s level 4 or lower Digimon."
